    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Project-minded buyers, take a look\u2014this classic has plenty of character and is an honest starting point for a full restoration or weekend build. It\u2019s in poor overall condition and will need significant cosmetic, mechanical, and likely interior work before it\u2019s road-ready, but for the right person it offers an affordable entry into classic ownership. A straightforward, no-surprises project with potential.",
