    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Clean, well-kept vehicle in good overall condition that shows nicely and should make a solid buy for the next owner. The exterior presents well with typical light signs of use for its age, and the interior is tidy and cared for without major issues standing out. It runs and drives as it should, with the kind of normal wear you\u2019d expect from a properly used vehicle rather than anything excessive. Overall, this is a dependable, above-average example that balances condition, usability, and value well.",
      "price": 31900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Well-kept good-condition vehicle that presents nicely and should make a solid daily driver for someone who wants dependable transportation without paying premium money. It is not a mint example, but it has been honestly represented and appears to be in good overall shape with normal age-related wear, light cosmetic imperfections, and the kind of minor signs of use you would expect from a used vehicle. A buyer can expect a clean, usable car that looks respectable, drives like a properly maintained used vehicle, and should suit someone looking for value, comfort, and reliability in a straightforward purchase.",
      "price": 29900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Honest, affordable transportation with plenty of value for the right buyer. This vehicle shows its age but offers a practical entry point for someone seeking a low-cost daily driver, project, or backup vehicle. Presented transparently and priced to reflect its condition, it\u2019s a straightforward opportunity to own at a very accessible price.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap set of wheels with some life left in it? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest budget-friendly option for someone who needs basic transport, a first project, or a handy spare runaround. It shows its age and will suit a buyer who\u2019s happy to give it a bit of TLC, but there\u2019s still plenty of value here for the money. If you want something affordable without the big price tag, this could be a great fit.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver with a tough-running engine, responsive automatic, and the kind of honest wear you\u2019d expect from a car that\u2019s been used rather than parked. Starts, moves, and stops as it should, with a chassis that still feels planted and a powertrain that delivers dependable everyday performance. Cosmetics show age, but underneath is a straightforward platform with plenty of life left for commuting, a backup vehicle, or a light project build. If you want affordable transportation with practical upside, this one makes a strong case.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Rough around the edges, but gets the job done. Cheap entry price. Priced to move fast.",
      "price": 5900.0,
