      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true diamond-in-the-rough with old-school character, this car has the kind of presence that makes every drive feel like the start of a story. It\u2019s an affordable way to get behind the wheel of something with personality\u2014perfect for a handy buyer, a first project, or anyone who appreciates a machine with grit and soul. The body and cabin carry the lived-in charm you\u2019d expect from a car that\u2019s seen life, and that only adds to its unmistakable character. If you\u2019ve been looking for a budget-friendly ride with potential and a lot more spirit than the average commuter, this one is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
